  "detailed_description": "Navigate an endless, ever-changing town whilst trying to make your way to Interstate 42 in this 3D psychological thriller.<br><br>As you drive, small anomalies appear - changes in the environment that challenge your perception and attention to detail. Take a Right Turn the moment you spot something wrong - each correct turn brings you closer to the exit.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/42d564f7a911be13dd8f92a5ed006776.poster.avif?t=1732998224\" width=590 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/42d564f7a911be13dd8f92a5ed006776.webm?t=1732998224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/42d564f7a911be13dd8f92a5ed006776.mp4?t=1732998224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But be warned - miss an anomaly or be sent to the void by one of the more aggressive hallucinations and you'll find yourself thrust back into the eerie loop.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/ea1b7da80cd7ad2b0e75447ce5db6489.poster.avif?t=1732998224\" width=590 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/ea1b7da80cd7ad2b0e75447ce5db6489.webm?t=1732998224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/ea1b7da80cd7ad2b0e75447ce5db6489.mp4?t=1732998224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>How long can you maintain your sanity in a town where reality constantly shifts, and the road to escape seems just out of reach?",
  "about_the_game": "Navigate an endless, ever-changing town whilst trying to make your way to Interstate 42 in this 3D psychological thriller.<br><br>As you drive, small anomalies appear - changes in the environment that challenge your perception and attention to detail. Take a Right Turn the moment you spot something wrong - each correct turn brings you closer to the exit.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/42d564f7a911be13dd8f92a5ed006776.poster.avif?t=1732998224\" width=590 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/42d564f7a911be13dd8f92a5ed006776.webm?t=1732998224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/42d564f7a911be13dd8f92a5ed006776.mp4?t=1732998224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But be warned - miss an anomaly or be sent to the void by one of the more aggressive hallucinations and you'll find yourself thrust back into the eerie loop.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/ea1b7da80cd7ad2b0e75447ce5db6489.poster.avif?t=1732998224\" width=590 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/ea1b7da80cd7ad2b0e75447ce5db6489.webm?t=1732998224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/ea1b7da80cd7ad2b0e75447ce5db6489.mp4?t=1732998224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>How long can you maintain your sanity in a town where reality constantly shifts, and the road to escape seems just out of reach?",
